{"words":[{"word":"club","count":4},{"word":"pity","count":3},{"word":"time","count":3},{"word":"winning","count":2},{"word":"any","count":2},{"word":"asked","count":2},{"word":"fan","count":2},{"word":"anita","count":2},{"word":"playername","count":2},{"word":"find","count":2},{"word":"strong","count":2},{"word":"expected","count":1},{"word":"hope","count":1},{"word":"thank","count":1},{"word":"holding","count":1},{"word":"giving","count":1},{"word":"victory","count":1},{"word":"cuts","count":1},{"word":"deeper","count":1},{"word":"loss","count":1},{"word":"real","count":1},{"word":"reason","count":1},{"word":"face","count":1},{"word":"kept","count":1},{"word":"seeing","count":1},{"word":"sympathy","count":1},{"word":"worse","count":1},{"word":"sense","count":1},{"word":"mocking","count":1},{"word":"everyone's","count":1},{"word":"eyes","count":1},{"word":"mean","count":1},{"word":"shake","count":1},{"word":"otherwise","count":1},{"word":"keep","count":1},{"word":"dueling","count":1},{"word":"last","count":1},{"word":"leader","count":1},{"word":"question","count":1},{"word":"point","count":1},{"word":"duelist","count":1},{"word":"fixated","count":1},{"word":"forget","count":1},{"word":"thrill","count":1},{"word":"duel","count":1},{"word":"heh","count":1},{"word":"answer","count":1},{"word":"worry","count":1},{"word":"give","count":1},{"word":"easily","count":1},{"word":"i'll","count":1},{"word":"everyone","count":1},{"word":"stop","count":1},{"word":"worrying","count":1},{"word":"wait","count":1},{"word":"secret","count":1},{"word":"h-hassle","count":1},{"word":"interest","count":1},{"word":"peaks","count":1},{"word":"prestige","count":1},{"word":"oh","count":1},{"word":"fine","count":1},{"word":"done","count":1},{"word":"thanks","count":1},{"word":"helping","count":1},{"word":"haha","count":1},{"word":"knew","count":1},{"word":"hidden","count":1},{"word":"powerhouse","count":1},{"word":"academy","count":1},{"word":"slack","count":1},{"word":"enough","count":1},{"word":"beat","count":1},{"word":"day","count":1},{"word":"taking","count":1},{"word":"title","count":1},{"word":"said","count":1},{"word":"professor","count":1},{"word":"calith","count":1},{"word":"arrange","count":1},{"word":"final","count":1},{"word":"showdown","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Just as expected. I had no hope of winning against you.","quest_name":"Welcome to the Fan Club","quest_id":181700015},{"text":"But... thank you. For not holding back. For not giving me a pity victory.","quest_name":"Welcome to the Fan Club","quest_id":181700015},{"text":"To me, pity cuts deeper than any loss. That's the real reason I couldn't face the club.","quest_name":"Welcome to the Fan Club","quest_id":181700015},{"text":"I kept seeing sympathy, pity, and worse... a sense of mocking in everyone's eyes. I know they didn't mean it that way, but I just couldn't shake it.","quest_name":"Welcome to the Fan Club","quest_id":181700015},{"text":"I know, otherwise they wouldn't have asked you to come here. But as you can see... I still need time to think about <i>why</i> I want to keep dueling.","quest_name":"Welcome to the Fan Club","quest_id":181700015},{"text":"The last time I was at the fan club, club leader Anita asked me a question.","quest_name":"Welcome to the Fan Club","quest_id":181700015},{"text":"\"What's the point of being a duelist if you're so fixated on winning that you forget the thrill of the duel itself?\"","quest_name":"Welcome to the Fan Club","quest_id":181700015},{"text":"Heh. I still don't have an answer for her.","quest_name":"Welcome to the Fan Club","quest_id":181700015},{"text":"Don't worry, {PlayerName}. I won't give up that easily. I'll find some time to go back and see everyone so they'll stop worrying.","quest_name":"Welcome to the Fan Club","quest_id":181700015},{"text":"...Wait!","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"I have to know... how did you get so strong? What's your secret?","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"...","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"...H-Hassle? Don't you have any interest in Peaks of Prestige at all?","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"...","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Oh, I'm fine. Well done, {PlayerName}. Thanks for helping our fan club.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Haha, who knew there was a hidden powerhouse like you at the Academy?","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"But that's not to say you can slack off. I may not be strong enough to beat you now, but one day, I'm taking back the title of No.2!","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"By the way, Anita said she'd go find Professor Calith to arrange the final showdown.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019}]}